4
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:36,840
Zang Hai, the Emperor has spoken.

5
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:42,490
Zang Hai, Assistant Supervisor of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau,

6
00:01:42,490 --> 00:01:47,300
is hereby honored for reinforcing the royal tomb, delivering hard work and high achievement.

7
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:50,840
As he is a man of great talent and a compatible birth date by astrology,

8
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:53,130
he is authorized to send the Empress Dowager's coffin for burial

9
00:01:53,130 --> 00:01:55,160
and reside in the royal tomb permanently...

10
00:01:56,640 --> 00:02:00,270
as a token of gratitude to the late emperor, Empress Dowager, and the court.

11
00:02:00,270 --> 00:02:01,300
Official.

12
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:03,900
Zang Hai is so young. How can he be buried?

13
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:06,510
He'll do well in the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

14
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:08,710
- Yes, Official. 
 - Official, please think twice.

15
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:11,330
Official Zang shouldn't be buried.

16
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:13,460
This is the intention of the leaders.

17
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:15,480
It also pains me to say so.

18
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:17,450
Given the conflicts of recent years,

19
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:20,050
the many flooding rivers, and earthquakes everywhere,

20
00:02:20,050 --> 00:02:23,430
are all because the world is not at peace.

21
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,370
The Imperial Astronomical Bureau has had its fortune told.

22
00:02:25,370 --> 00:02:27,980
For the stability of the world and peace everywhere,

23
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:31,180
Zang Hai is the most suitable choice.

24
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:35,640
It's an honor others couldn't receive, even if they wanted it.

25
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,770
- Official. 
 - Official.

26
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:39,460
- Official. 
 - Duly noted.

27
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:41,840
I'm willing to sacrifice myself for the Empress Dowager.

28
00:02:46,770 --> 00:02:48,340
Very good.

29
00:02:54,830 --> 00:02:56,930
Congratulations, Zang Hai.

30
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:59,830
It's a great honor.

31
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:12,300
Official Zang.

32
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,300
Official Zang.

33
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,980
Why would you want to be buried alive with us?

34
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:17,330
Why did you agree so readily?

35
00:03:17,330 --> 00:03:18,920
- That's right. 
 - That's right.

36
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:21,000
That's right, Official.

37
00:03:22,260 --> 00:03:27,790
A man who is too talented will become a thorn in the side of others

38
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:29,610
and need to endure their scorn.

39
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:34,070
Thus, they deliberately arranged for you to build the tomb.

40
00:03:34,070 --> 00:03:39,800
But it looks like you'd already guessed that.

41
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:42,430
Chu Huaiming's intentions are not hard to guess,

42
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:44,580
but I didn't expect...

43
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:48,050
that you all volunteered to be martyred?

44
00:03:48,050 --> 00:03:50,090
Don't you want to think twice?

45
00:03:50,770 --> 00:03:52,770
If we didn't agree to,

46
00:03:52,770 --> 00:03:58,300
they'd ask again and again until we agreed.

47
00:03:58,300 --> 00:04:01,430
In the end, we still wouldn't be able to escape

48
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:03,930
being forced to volunteer with our limbs destroyed.

49
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:11,070
The climate among the imperial court has already come to such a level?

50
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:13,800
Although the Great Yong Dynasty's founding emperors

51
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:17,170
had long ago placed a ban on live burials,

52
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:21,500
but that didn't stop some of those from doing it forcibly.

53
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:25,650
Everyone should be loyal, so who would dare to refuse?

54
00:04:25,650 --> 00:04:30,330
Of course, they were forced, but it got framed as volunteering.

55
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:34,020
As for Chu Huaiming, he was even more blatant.

56
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:38,800
He could use it to claim credit and enrich himself.

57
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,730
Enrich himself?

58
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:47,620
The court spends a lot of money

59
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:50,460
to honor those who will be buried.

60
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:53,770
We are all going to die,

61
00:04:53,770 --> 00:04:56,720
so we can exchange our lives for some money

62
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:59,430
to help our families and children survive.

63
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:04,530
Although the money will be stolen by Chu Huaiming and the others,

64
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:08,190
and in the end, there won't be much left,

65
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:14,850
this money is still life-saving for our families.

66
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:19,220
However, Zang Hai,

67
00:05:20,260 --> 00:05:22,820
you are so young and talented.

68
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:25,340
Why are you willing to die?

69
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:36,680
I'm as miserable as everyone else.

70
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:44,140
Heaven and hell are all similar,

71
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:48,040
so we'll treat it as wandering to a foreign land.

72
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:55,940
Come on.

73
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:58,650
Let's drink.

74
00:05:58,650 --> 00:06:03,820
Let's get heavily drunk today and die calmly tomorrow.

75
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:05,090
Drink!

76
00:06:05,090 --> 00:06:06,780
Drink!

77
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:24,580
- Come on. 
 - Come on.

78
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:27,190
- Come on. 
 - Come on.

79
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,630
Fill it up.

80
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:30,500
Come on.

81
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:31,800
Come on.

82
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,870
Together.

83
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:14,170
Come on. Let's drink.

84
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,820
- Come on. 
 - Let's drink.

85
00:07:22,410 --> 00:07:23,900
Come on.

86
